"line":29},{"w":"there's","s":215.68,"e":216,"line":29},{"w":"a","s":216,"e":216.5,"line":29},{"w":"wormhole","s":216.5,"e":216.84,"line":29},{"w":"out","s":216.84,"e":217.88,"line":29},{"w":"there","s":217.88,"e":219.04,"line":29},{"w":"I'm","s":219.04,"e":219.6,"line":29},{"w":"gonna","s":219.6,"e":219.74,"line":29},{"w":"find","s":219.74,"e":220.22,"line":29},{"w":"it","s":220.22,"e":220.5,"line":29},{"w":"now","s":220.5,"e":220.89,"line":29}],"lines":[{"s":15.72,"e":21.96,"text":"I left the dark at dawn With a duffel and a chart"},{"s":23.16,"e":30.32,"text":"You laughed and waved goodbye From the stern with a paper heart"},{"s":30.84,"e":36.68,"text":"The captain said, stay close But I like the edge of things"},{"s":37.54,"e":43.82,"text":"I want the kind of map That bends where the blue sea splits"},{"s":46.22,"e":50.2,"text":"Three points on the compass Keep spinning out of line"},{"s":50.28,"e":53.92,"text":"Clouds hang like a warning Still I feel that pull inside"},{"s":53.92,"e":57.24,"text":"The water starts to whisper And the horizon folds in two"},{"s":57.24,"e":61.08,"text":"I'm already halfway gone When I'm moving toward the blue"},{"s":61.08,"e":65.68,"text":"Take me down, take me down To the Bermuda Sound"},{"s":66.68,"e":75.08,"text":"I'm sailing for the sea Where the whole world comes unbound"},{"s":75.68,"e":80.28,"text":"Take me down, take me down Past the charts and the crowds"},{"s":81.68,"e":87.72,"text":"If there's a wormhole out there I'm gonna find it now"},{"s":88.8,"e":94.88,"text":"We passed erect grey buoys And a school of silver bones"},{"s":95.68,"e":102.68,"text":"The radio went static Then it sang in undertones"},{"s":103.46,"e":110.1,"text":"A ringer from a pier Where the waves should have stayed flat"},{"s":110.24,"e":117.68,"text":"My crew in pale and quiet I just smiled and stared right back"},{"s":119,"e":122.92,"text":"Three points on the compass Keep spinning out of line"},{"s":122.92,"e":126.6,"text":"Clouds hang like a warning Still I feel that pull inside"},{"s":126.6,"e":129.98,"text":"The water starts to whisper And the horizon folds in two"},{"s":129.98,"e":133.6,"text":"I'm already halfway gone When I'm moving toward the blue"},{"s":133.6,"e":138.26,"text":"Take me down, take me down To the Bermuda Sound"},{"s":139.2,"e":147.9,"text":"I'm sailing for the sea Where the whole world comes unbound"},{"s":152.92,"e":159.92,"text":"Take me down, if there's a wormhole out there I'm gonna find it now"},{"s":176.92,"e":180.26,"text":"There's a door in the deep And it's open and slow"},{"s":180.26,"e":184.18,"text":"I see my name in the spray I see tomorrow glow"},{"s":184.18,"e":193.1,"text":"Hold the line, hold the line We're falling through the tide"},{"s":194.26,"e":199.5,"text":"Take me down, take me down To the Bermuda Sound"},{"s":200.64,"e":208.56,"text":"I'm sailing for the sea Where the whole world comes unbound"},{"s":208.56,"e":213.86,"text":"Take me down, take me down Past the charts and the crowds"},{"s":214.9,"e":220.56,"text":"If there's a wormhole out there I'm gonna find it now"}],"duration":237.8800048828125,"source":"whisper","generatedAt":"2026-05-22T02:28:31.181Z","model":"whisper-1"}